title: torch.Softmax only accepts 2D tensors
body_html: The documentation says it can accept a tensor of any dimension and input dimensions and output dimensions match. However, when you give it a 1D tensor, it says it expects 2D tensor. I am using pytorch with python3 and ubuntu 16.04.
